name: Silver Pendant, Citrine and Strawberry Quartz Necklace
description:
This beautiful necklace is made with citrine stones in their natural shape and "strawberry" colored quartz nuggets. The pendant is a solid silver plaque hanging from a large "strawberry" quartz nugget. All this beautiful stones are put together making links with silver wire. It has a hook closure and it is 19" long.

This piece comes inside a signature Elie's Papel cotton canvas bag

name: Amethyst, Mother of Pearl, Strawberry Quartz, Red Quartz and Faux-Pearl
description:
This beautiful necklace is made with Amethyst nuggets, Mother of Pearl pieces, round Red Quartz beads, "strawberry" colored quartz, and Faux-Pearls with light blue beads at the end. All these beautiful stones are put together making links with silver wire. It has a hook closure and it is 20" long.

This piece comes inside a signature Elie's Papel cotton canvas bag. For more pictures check my Facebook page  or the Elie's Papel blog.

name: Red Coral, Mother of Pearl, Red Quartz, and Strawberry Quartz Necklace
description:
This beautiful necklace is made with Red Coral nuggets, mother of pearl round and irregular beads, and "strawberry" colored quartz. All these beautiful stones are put together making links with silver wire and loops with silver seed beads. It has a hook closure and it is 28" long.

This piece comes inside a signature Elie's Papel cotton canvas bag. For more pictures check my Facebook page  or the Elie's Papel blog

name: Chandelier Academy Awards Style
description:
This greeting card was designed especially for an event I attended for the 2009 Academy Awards Gifting Suite. These are Limited Edition and printed on environmentally friendly paper. The envelope is 30% recycled paper content

They come in sets of 6 inside a drawstring reusable cotton canvas bag. Each card measures 3.5" x 4.875" and come with matching white envelope.

For more information on the event go to http://eliespapel.blogspot.com/2009/02/job-well-done.html
